<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Payment Failed — Action Required</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f7f9fb;
      color: #222;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 620px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 14px;
      box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0077ff, #0044cc);
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 28px 20px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 35px 30px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: #111;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #0077ff;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #777;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 25px;
      background: #f3f5f7;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Payment Failed — Action Required</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h1>We couldn’t process your renewal payment</h1>
      <p>Hi {{adminName}},</p>
      <p>We attempted to renew your <strong>{{planName}}</strong> plan, but your payment did not go through.</p>

      <p>To ensure uninterrupted access to your institution’s account and data, please update your payment method or retry the transaction.</p>

      <p>Don’t worry — your account and athlete data remain safe and secure for the next <strong>7 days</strong>. After that, your plan may be temporarily paused until payment is completed.</p>

      <a href="{{retryLink}}" class="btn">Retry Payment</a>

      <p>If you’ve already made the payment, please ignore this message — your plan will reactivate automatically once confirmed.</p>

      <p>Thank you for staying with us,<br>
      <strong>The Project Athlete 360 Team</strong></p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      © {{currentYear}} Project Athlete 360. All rights reserved.<br/>
      You’re receiving this email because you have an active account with Project Athlete 360.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>